# SHA-256 pins for the OFFICIAL elrepo-built el8 kernel-ml RPMs consumed in mirror mode (ADR-087).
# Vetted: downloaded over HTTPS from the official elrepo mirror (coreix elrepo-archive-archive); each RPM
# carries elrepo's GPG signature (key 51600989, signed 2026-01-23 = the 6.12.11 release). elrepo rotated
# that key and no longer publishes it, so full GPG verify isn't possible — these pins are the integrity
# anchor: build-rpm.sh fails the build if a downloaded RPM's SHA-256 does not match here, BEFORE re-signing
# with the Datacosmos key. Update only when adding a new version, re-vetting the source.
